trans-unit.source: The PartialResultProcessing enumeration specifies the required type of partial results processing.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen PartialResultProcessing angir nødvendige delvise resultater behandling.

trans-unit.source: An application performing an asynchronous operation can use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.BeginSendRequest%2A> method, <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.EndSendRequest%2A> method, and (optionally) the <xref:System.AsyncCallback> delegate in the standard .NET style.
trans-unit.target: Et program som utfører en asynkron operasjon kan bruke den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.BeginSendRequest%2A>metoden <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.EndSendRequest%2A>metoden, og (valgfritt) i <xref:System.AsyncCallback>delegere i standard .NET-stil.</xref:System.AsyncCallback> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.EndSendRequest%2A> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.BeginSendRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: An application retrieving partial results can call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.BeginSendRequest%2A> and pass either ReturnPartialResults or ReturnPartialResultsAndNotifyCallback as the `partialMode` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Et program som henter delvise resultater kan kalle den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.BeginSendRequest%2A>og sende ReturnPartialResults eller ReturnPartialResultsAndNotifyCallback som den `partialMode` parameteren.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.LdapConnection.BeginSendRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: In most scenarios, use NoPartialResultSupport for better performance and scalability.
trans-unit.target: Bruk NoPartialResultSupport for bedre ytelsen og skalerbarheten i de fleste tilfeller.

trans-unit.source: The use of ReturnPartialResults or ReturnPartialResultsAndNotifyCallback is only recommended in the scenario where the retrieval of partial results is desired.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av ReturnPartialResults eller ReturnPartialResultsAndNotifyCallback anbefales bare i scenario der henting av delvise resultater ønskes.

trans-unit.source: For example, when performing a search with the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryNotificationControl> specified, the search results are returned only when changes are made to that object.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel når du utfører et søk med den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryNotificationControl>er angitt, søkeresultatene returneres bare når endringer av objektet.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryNotificationControl>

trans-unit.source: The search never completes and partial results are returned.
trans-unit.target: Søket er ikke fullført, og delvise resultater.

trans-unit.source: The application will not retrieve partial results.
trans-unit.target: Programmet kan ikke hente delvise resultater.

trans-unit.source: The application will retrieve partial results.
An application will retrieve partial results and use the callback mechanism.
trans-unit.target: Et program henter delvise resultater og bruke tilbakeringing mekanisme.
